      "content": "i don't even know why i'm typing this. i just feel like i've completely hit a wall. after 5 years of this phd, the funding just... it's gone. the lab is basically empty now. i look at my desk and i just feel nothing. no motivation, no future, just this massive, heavy emptiness. it feels like i wasted my entire life for a version of myself that doesn't even exist anymore. i'm just so incredibly tired of trying to fight for something that clearly isn't meant to be.",
