      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a heavy way to put it... \"a ghost.\" it feels true though. like i'm just going through the motions of a life that doesn't even belong to me anymore. everything i thought i was building is just... gone. it’s like there’s no way to actually fix it, just a long, slow decline. i just want the noise to stop. i just want to be able to rest without feeling this crushing pressure to fix everything. i'm so exhausted.",
